Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.87,0:01:36.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let up! You've got to hold \Nout until everyone's evacuated!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.66,0:01:37.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:47.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:50.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's evacuated!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:59.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they actually possess a \Npower that can oppose us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:02.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:24.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.92,0:02:27.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Joey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:29.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,0:02:31.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:36.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If not, then we need to think one up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:37.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:41.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't destroy those \Nspheres with normal attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:45.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Heroman's repeated attacks \Ndidn't even scratch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:47.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should know that better than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:50.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:54.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And Heroman's taken considerable damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:56.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also worried about your stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.91,0:03:00.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying to do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:03.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll return for now, and \Nthink up a new plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:04.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:13.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:17.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.95,0:03:25.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why those...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.15,0:03:28.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Will...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:29.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:33.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's gonna happen to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:35.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:40.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they'll put us on trial or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:43.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we can bribe them to get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:44.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I seriously doubt that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:48.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll be executed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.97,0:03:50.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:53.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If they wanted to do that, we \Nwouldn't have been locked up in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:55.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what'll happen to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:58.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.46,0:04:07.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never going to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:09.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home, alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:10.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:27.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To think this planet hid an enemy with \Nthis level of combat ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:30.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However there only seems to be a single one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.82,0:04:34.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It does not surpass our own attack strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.93,0:04:39.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So there is only one thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:44.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:49.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can get out that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.52,0:04:50.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:54.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:55.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:02.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nick!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:05.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:07.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:21.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... We didn't come here to rebel \Nagainst you at all, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:22.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nick...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:25.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.61,0:05:28.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything you could tell us \Nwould be just great...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:29.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nick!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:31.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What else can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:33.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all your fault anyway, Will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:34.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:35.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.61,0:05:37.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:39.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be quiet now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:36.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Heroman okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:37.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.57,0:06:39.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I replaced the broken parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:43.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, how are {\i1}you{\i0}, Joey?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:44.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:50.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange... When Heroman \Ngot big I felt really tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:52.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:56.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Professor, what should we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.13,0:06:59.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The power's out so we can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:00.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Worry not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.74,0:07:05.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought something like this might happen, \Nso I installed a personal power generator.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:09.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Joey... Are you sure \Nyou're feeling okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:11.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Just spiffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:13.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:23.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A bicycle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:26.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, pedal it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:34.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good, Joey. Keep going like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:36.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:40.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, what are you planning on doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:42.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to come up with a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:45.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to do that, you can't neglect \Ninformation gathering and analysis!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:48.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:50.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But what are you doing, specifically?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:08:01.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First up is hacking and \Ncommunications interception!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:08.45,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the 21st armored division reporting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:11.35,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,We are currently deployed to \Nthe suburbs of Center City.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:14.01,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,We are guiding evacuees, and have \Ntaken a defensive position.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:16.62,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,We have nothing else to report at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:17.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:31.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Communications have ceased \Nfrom the seventh squad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:33.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Secure the citizens' evacuation routes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.25,0:08:34.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare for battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:35.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:36.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:07.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.07,0:09:09.78,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even a scratch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:11.22,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.22,0:09:12.50,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep up the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:15.34,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming... All hands, retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:34.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:36.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't rush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.17,0:09:38.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I need more information!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:45.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am now at the suburbs of Center City!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:49.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at this scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:54.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The five giant spheres that \Nhave been released
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:58.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,are each progressing straight ahead in one \Ndirection, oblivious to the military's attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:04.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Skrugg's UFO appeared suddenly from the \Nsky and began to attack Center City...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:07.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What could be their purpose behind this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.38,0:10:11.75,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to keep a close \Nwatch on their movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:13.89,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,We want everyone to see what's really happen-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:16.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Verify that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:21.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us, but we've received some \Nnew information during the report.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:25.27,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,There are new developments at Center City.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:28.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm reporting from on top of a \Nbuilding in front of the factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:32.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Skrugg troops are emerging from the \Nfactory that the Skrugg have occupied.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.29,0:10:33.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And in incredible numbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:38.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat: Skrugg soldiers are coming down \Nfrom the factory one after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:44.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Skrugg are making another move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:48.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. What are they planning now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.05,0:10:49.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.41,0:10:57.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just stay here doing nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:10:59.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.06,0:11:00.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.59,0:11:05.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:09.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't leave the Skrugg \Nto do whatever they want!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.08,0:11:10.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:13.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I should at least be able to \Nattract their attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:15.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.06,0:11:16.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Psy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:21.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's exactly as you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:26.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to come up with a plan to deal \Nwith those spheres if possible, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:33.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A guitar?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.70,0:11:35.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to be for, Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.81,0:11:38.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to stop them with rock 'n' roll?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:42.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that this is nothing but a \Nguitar, but there's a secret hidden here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.98,0:11:45.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a normal speaker, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:48.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no... That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:53.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In here is the amplification device that \Nwas installed in that weapon of theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.87,0:11:55.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.84,0:11:58.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Think back...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:12:04.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Their weapon was able to create that \Npowerful an air vortex from absolutely nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:09.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Using that amplification \Ndevice, I successfully...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:13.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...amplified sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:15.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... very impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:19.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But what's the point to go \Nthrough all the trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:21.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A reasonable question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:24.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is a very good reason, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:29.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is merely conjecture, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:34.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but they may communicate among themselves \Nusing high-frequency sound waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:36.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is also merely conjecture,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:41.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but their hearing may also be able to detect \Nsound from a much wider range than humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:43.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I've surmised!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:46.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:52.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going up against the Skrugg, this \Nguitar is more of a super powerful weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:56.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...than missiles or cannons!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:04.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay? I'm going to continue \Nanalyzing those spheres.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.82,0:13:07.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.54,0:13:08.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.77,0:13:09.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:11.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:14.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta do what we gotta do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:16.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:53.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, Joey?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:56.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna play hit and away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:59.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't go up head-to-head \Nagainst those kind of numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:02.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you beat the enemy, hide \Nyourself and move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:05.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let them get a bead on our location.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:08.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That way we're sure to thin \Nout their numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.38,0:14:09.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:18.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:20.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:50.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:53.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:15:00.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cross my heart and hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:13.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? That's surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:16.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The professor's invention actually worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:18.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:31.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hostilities have broken out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.89,0:15:33.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to be that white one of interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:36.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Dispatch reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.46,0:15:38.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll finish this right at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:40.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Display the location.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:41.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:43.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.09,0:15:46.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they are using the wrecked buildings
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:49.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and passageways we are not aware \Nof to keep on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:53.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot pinpoint the \Nenemy's precise location.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:55.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:16:00.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our losses are already greater than 14.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:03.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Using the terrain to your \Nadvantage? What impudence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:06.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, it's an eye for an eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:21.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:24.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:29.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:32.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous, you have to hurry and escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.52,0:16:36.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother's gone, so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:41.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, hide yourself here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:44.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come and pick you up \Nafter the battle's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:45.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:48.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Joey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:50.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me along!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.37,0:16:51.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:55.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be dangerous no matter where I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.63,0:16:59.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So staying next to you and Heroman \Nis the safest place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:01.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:04.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to search for my \Nbrother, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:05.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:07.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:13.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You just can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:14.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:18.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I am, then protect me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:23.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Joey?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:27.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Joey, what are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.39,0:17:28.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.75,0:17:30.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're here too, Psy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:31.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.72,0:17:33.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting more confident by the second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.43,0:17:35.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:52.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:17:59.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:02.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:14.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:17.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...a different kind of Skrugg than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:19.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:20.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:22.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't face them all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:25.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:48.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Joey?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:51.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:54.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, then let's try this again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:10.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, how?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:17.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina, Psy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:21.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot, there goes our escape route!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:38.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it... It's different than \Nthe enemies from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:19:59.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.41,0:20:01.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:24.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey, behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:37.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this one to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.22,0:20:39.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys bust up that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:40.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:43.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.94,0:20:45.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:03.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's planning on taking it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.72,0:21:10.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:11.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:36.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It actually blocked...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:37.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Heroman's attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:56.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.24,0:22:13.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:24.09,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,"Can you hear this voice?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.09,0:22:31.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been calling that, always, from deep within my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.37,0:22:45.46,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you, all alone, let another lonely one be next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.46,0:22:51.01,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Because together it's not lonely, it's twoly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.01,0:22:56.14,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,See, you're not alone any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.28,0:22:59.99,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because there's no one next to me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.99,0:23:02.54,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't mean that I'm lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.54,0:23:07.74,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,For someone to notice this pain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:13.27,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,that heart must have surely cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.27,0:23:16.65,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we'll crush to bits
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.65,0:23:20.35,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,the fortress of our limitless sadness!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.35,0:23:24.05,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.05,0:23:27.73,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it? I'm running through at full power.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.73,0:23:31.47,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,To where you're waiting, left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:34.64,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,in the place of tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.95,0:23:39.77,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in you, with burning passion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:43.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.77,0:23:52.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Heroman:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.71,0:23:55.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But... we still have to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.65,0:23:59.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The identity of the assassins are Lina's \Nbrother Will and his best friend Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:04.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey and the others retreat, able to do \Nnothing against their modified bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.42,0:24:06.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey cannot hide his trembling,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.79,0:24:11.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but in front of the Skrugg's unrelenting \Ninvasion they are forced to make a new decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.29,0:24:16.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Heroman Episode #6: Backlash!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.01,0:24:17.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.65,0:24:19.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
